com.perforce.p4java.server

Class Fingerprint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.perforce.p4java.server.Fingerprint

  • public class Fingerprint
extends Object
    Object representing the three parts of a Perforce fingerprint, the server address, the user name, and the ticket token value.

    Note: currently the user portion should be "******" as it is not used.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Fingerprint()
      Creates an empty fingerprint
      Fingerprint(String serverAddress, String userName, String fingerprintValue)
